vfsStream is used for unit testing file I/O functions.

See https://github.com/mikey179/vfsStream and http://vfs.bovigo.org/
for more details.

To install vfsStream, Composer (a tool for dependency managment in PHP) is
required.

See http://getcomposer.org/doc/00-intro.md for more details.

In short, run the following command in this directory (dependencies):
php composer.phar install